safetyTips: Home delivery orders and payment are taken over the phone. If you are self-isolating, then let us know. The shop and kitchen (where our heat-and-eat meals are prepared) both have the top hygiene rating of 5 and we are taking all recommended additional precautions.
name: Jenkins & Son
description: Jenkins and Son the fishmongers delivers fish and heat-and-eat dishes free to the local area. Call to order. Free home delivery on Wednesday, Thursday, Friday and Saturday to Deal, Sandwich and Dover area (min order £25) and to Folkestone, Canterbury and Thanet area (min order £50)
